{
  "video_id": "Gj8IA6xOpSk",
  "title": "The call to learn | Clifford Stoll",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12160.0,
      "end_time": 14160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m delighted to be here."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14160.0,
      "end_time": 17160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m honored by the invitation, and thanks."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17160.0,
      "end_time": 20160.0,
      "text": "I would love to talk about stuff that I&#39;m interested in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20160.0,
      "end_time": 22160.0,
      "text": "but unfortunately, I suspect that what I&#39;m interested in"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22160.0,
      "end_time": 25160.0,
      "text": "won&#39;t interest many other people."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25160.0,
      "end_time": 27160.0,
      "text": "First off, my badge says I&#39;m an astronomer."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27160.0,
      "end_time": 29160.0,
      "text": "I would love to talk about my astronomy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 29160.0,
      "end_time": 32159.0,
      "text": "but I suspect that the number of people who are interested in radiative transfer"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32159.0,
      "end_time": 34160.0,
      "text": "in non-gray atmospheres"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34160.0,
      "end_time": 36160.0,
      "text": "and polarization of light in Jupiter&#39;s upper atmosphere"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 36160.0,
      "end_time": 38160.0,
      "text": "are the number of people who&#39;d fit in a bus shelter."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 38160.0,
      "end_time": 40160.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m not going to talk about that."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 40160.0,
      "end_time": 42160.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 42160.0,
      "end_time": 44160.0,
      "text": "It would be just as much fun"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 44160.0,
      "end_time": 47160.0,
      "text": "to talk about some stuff that happened in 1986 and 1987,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 47160.0,
      "end_time": 50160.0,
      "text": "when a computer hacker is breaking into our systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 50160.0,
      "end_time": 52160.0,
      "text": "over at Lawrence Berkeley Labs."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 52160.0,
      "end_time": 54160.0,
      "text": "And I caught the guys,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 54160.0,
      "end_time": 58160.0,
      "text": "and they turned out to be working for what was then the Soviet KGB,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 58160.0,
      "end_time": 60160.0,
      "text": "and stealing information and selling it."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 60160.0,
      "end_time": 64160.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;d love to talk about that -- and it&#39;d be fun --"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 64160.0,
      "end_time": 67160.0,
      "text": "but, 20 years later ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 67160.0,
      "end_time": 69160.0,
      "text": "I find computer security, frankly, to be kind of boring."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 69160.0,
      "end_time": 71160.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s tedious."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 71160.0,
      "end_time": 72160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m --"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 72160.0,
      "end_time": 75160.0,
      "text": "The first time you do something, it&#39;s science."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 76160.0,
      "end_time": 79160.0,
      "text": "The second time, it&#39;s engineering."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 79160.0,
      "end_time": 82160.0,
      "text": "A third time, it&#39;s just being a technician."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 82160.0,
      "end_time": 85160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a scientist. Once I do something, I do something else."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 85160.0,
      "end_time": 87160.0,
      "text": "So, I&#39;m not going to talk about that."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 87160.0,
      "end_time": 94160.0,
      "text": "Nor am I going to talk about what I think are obvious statements from my first book,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 94160.0,
      "end_time": 97160.0,
      "text": "\"Silicon Snake Oil,\" or my second book,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 98160.0,
      "end_time": 100160.0,
      "text": "nor am I going to talk about"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 100160.0,
      "end_time": 102160.0,
      "text": "why I believe computers don&#39;t belong in schools."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 103160.0,
      "end_time": 107160.0,
      "text": "I feel that there&#39;s a massive and bizarre idea going around"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 107160.0,
      "end_time": 111160.0,
      "text": "that we have to bring more computers into schools."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 111160.0,
      "end_time": 113160.0,
      "text": "My idea is: no! No!"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 113160.0,
      "end_time": 117160.0,
      "text": "Get them out of schools, and keep them out of schools."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 117160.0,
      "end_time": 119160.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;d love to talk about this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 119160.0,
      "end_time": 124160.0,
      "text": "but I think the argument is so obvious to anyone who&#39;s hung around a fourth grade classroom"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 124160.0,
      "end_time": 128160.0,
      "text": "that it doesn&#39;t need much talking about --"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 128160.0,
      "end_time": 130160.0,
      "text": "but I guess I may be very wrong about that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 130160.0,
      "end_time": 131160.0,
      "text": "and everything else that I&#39;ve said."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 131160.0,
      "end_time": 133160.0,
      "text": "So don&#39;t go back and read my dissertation."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 133160.0,
      "end_time": 135160.0,
      "text": "It probably has lies in it as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 135160.0,
      "end_time": 139160.0,
      "text": "Having said that, I outlined my talk about five minutes ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 139160.0,
      "end_time": 142160.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 142160.0,
      "end_time": 144160.0,
      "text": "And if you look at it over here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 144160.0,
      "end_time": 147160.0,
      "text": "the main thing I wrote on my thumb was the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 147160.0,
      "end_time": 150160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m supposed to talk about the future, yes?"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 150160.0,
      "end_time": 157160.0,
      "text": "Oh, right. And my feeling is, asking me to talk about the future is bizarre,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 157160.0,
      "end_time": 159160.0,
      "text": "because I&#39;ve got gray hair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 159160.0,
      "end_time": 165160.0,
      "text": "and so, it&#39;s kind of silly for me to talk about the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 165160.0,
      "end_time": 169160.0,
      "text": "In fact, I think that if you really want to know what the future&#39;s going to be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 169160.0,
      "end_time": 171160.0,
      "text": "if you really want to know about the future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 171160.0,
      "end_time": 175160.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t ask a technologist, a scientist, a physicist."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 175160.0,
      "end_time": 179160.0,
      "text": "No! Don&#39;t ask somebody who&#39;s writing code."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 182160.0,
      "end_time": 187160.0,
      "text": "No, if you want to know what society&#39;s going to be like in 20 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 187160.0,
      "end_time": 189160.0,
      "text": "ask a kindergarten teacher."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 189160.0,
      "end_time": 192160.0,
      "text": "They know."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 192160.0,
      "end_time": 195160.0,
      "text": "In fact, don&#39;t ask just any kindergarten teacher,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 195160.0,
      "end_time": 197160.0,
      "text": "ask an experienced one."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 197160.0,
      "end_time": 201160.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re the ones who know what society is going to be like in another generation."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 201160.0,
      "end_time": 203160.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t. Nor, I suspect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 203160.0,
      "end_time": 206160.0,
      "text": "do many other people who are talking about what the future will bring."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 206160.0,
      "end_time": 210160.0,
      "text": "Certainly, all of us can imagine these cool new things"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 210160.0,
      "end_time": 211160.0,
      "text": "that are going to be there."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 211160.0,
      "end_time": 215160.0,
      "text": "But to me, things aren&#39;t the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 215160.0,
      "end_time": 218160.0,
      "text": "What I ask myself is, what&#39;s society is going to be like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 218160.0,
      "end_time": 224160.0,
      "text": "when the kids today are phenomenally good at text messaging"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 224160.0,
      "end_time": 227160.0,
      "text": "and spend a huge amount of on-screen time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 227160.0,
      "end_time": 232160.0,
      "text": "but have never gone bowling together?"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 233160.0,
      "end_time": 236160.0,
      "text": "Change is happening, and the change that is happening"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 236160.0,
      "end_time": 238160.0,
      "text": "is not one that is in software."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 239160.0,
      "end_time": 240160.0,
      "text": "But that&#39;s not what I&#39;m going to talk about."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 240160.0,
      "end_time": 243160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d love to talk about it, it&#39;d be fun,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 243160.0,
      "end_time": 246160.0,
      "text": "but I want to talk about what I&#39;m doing now. What am I doing now?"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 246160.0,
      "end_time": 248160.0,
      "text": "Oh -- the other thing that I think I&#39;d like to talk about"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 248160.0,
      "end_time": 251160.0,
      "text": "is right over here. Right over here."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 252160.0,
      "end_time": 258159.0,
      "text": "Is that visible? What I&#39;d like to talk about is one-sided things."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 258160.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260160.00000000003,
      "text": "I would dearly love to talk about"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 260160.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263160.0,
      "text": "things that have one side."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 263160.0,
      "end_time": 267160.0,
      "text": "Because I love Mobius loops. I not only love Mobius loops,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 267160.0,
      "end_time": 270160.0,
      "text": "but I&#39;m one of the very few people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 270160.0,
      "end_time": 273160.0,
      "text": "if not the only person in the world, that makes Klein bottles."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 273160.0,
      "end_time": 276160.0,
      "text": "Right away, I hope that all of your eyes glaze over."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 276160.0,
      "end_time": 279160.0,
      "text": "This is a Klein bottle."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 279160.0,
      "end_time": 282160.0,
      "text": "For those of you in the audience who know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 282160.0,
      "end_time": 284160.0,
      "text": "you roll your eyes and say, yup, I know all about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 284160.0,
      "end_time": 286160.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s one sided. It&#39;s a bottle whose inside is its outside."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 286160.0,
      "end_time": 289160.0,
      "text": "It has zero volume. And it&#39;s non-orientable."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 289160.0,
      "end_time": 291160.0,
      "text": "It has wonderful properties."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 291160.0,
      "end_time": 293160.0,
      "text": "If you take two Mobius loops and sew their common edge together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 293160.0,
      "end_time": 296160.0,
      "text": "you get one of these, and I make them out of glass."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 296160.0,
      "end_time": 298160.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;d love to talk to you about this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 298160.0,
      "end_time": 302160.0,
      "text": "but I don&#39;t have much in the way of ... things to say because --"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 304160.0,
      "end_time": 306160.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 306160.0,
      "end_time": 307160.0,
      "text": "(Chris Anderson: I&#39;ve got a cold.)"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 307160.0,
      "end_time": 314160.0,
      "text": "However, the \"D\" in TED of course stands for design."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 314160.0,
      "end_time": 316160.0,
      "text": "Just two weeks ago I made --"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 316160.0,
      "end_time": 322160.0,
      "text": "you know, I&#39;ve been making small, medium and big Klein bottles for the trade."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 322160.0,
      "end_time": 326160.0,
      "text": "But what I&#39;ve just made --"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 326160.0,
      "end_time": 329160.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m delighted to show you, first time in public here."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 335160.0,
      "end_time": 340160.0,
      "text": "This is a Klein bottle wine bottle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 340160.0,
      "end_time": 343160.0,
      "text": "which, although in four dimensions"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 343160.0,
      "end_time": 346160.0,
      "text": "it shouldn&#39;t be able to hold any fluid at all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 346160.0,
      "end_time": 348160.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s perfectly capable of doing so"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 348160.0,
      "end_time": 350160.0,
      "text": "because our universe has only three spatial dimensions."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 350160.0,
      "end_time": 353160.0,
      "text": "And because our universe is only three spatial dimensions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 353160.0,
      "end_time": 355160.0,
      "text": "it can hold fluids."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 356160.0,
      "end_time": 361160.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s highly -- that one&#39;s the cool one."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 361160.0,
      "end_time": 366160.0,
      "text": "That was a month of my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 366160.0,
      "end_time": 370160.0,
      "text": "But although I would love to talk about topology with you, I&#39;m not going to."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 371160.0,
      "end_time": 377160.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 377160.0,
      "end_time": 382160.0,
      "text": "Instead, I&#39;m going to mention my mom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 382160.0,
      "end_time": 385160.0,
      "text": "who passed away last summer."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 385160.0,
      "end_time": 388160.0,
      "text": "Had collected photographs of me, as mothers will do."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 388160.0,
      "end_time": 390160.0,
      "text": "Could somebody put this guy up?"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 390160.0,
      "end_time": 394160.0,
      "text": "And I looked over her album"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 394160.0,
      "end_time": 397160.0,
      "text": "and she had collected a picture of me, standing --"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 397160.0,
      "end_time": 401160.0,
      "text": "well, sitting -- in 1969, in front of a bunch of dials."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 402160.0,
      "end_time": 405160.0,
      "text": "And I looked at it, and said, oh my god,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 405160.0,
      "end_time": 407160.0,
      "text": "that was me, when I was working at the electronic music studio!"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 407160.0,
      "end_time": 410160.0,
      "text": "As a technician, repairing and maintaining"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 411160.0,
      "end_time": 415160.0,
      "text": "the electronic music studio at SUNY Buffalo. And wow!"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 415160.0,
      "end_time": 420160.0,
      "text": "Way back machine. And I said to myself, oh yeah!"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 421160.0,
      "end_time": 423160.0,
      "text": "And it sent me back."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 425160.0,
      "end_time": 432160.0,
      "text": "Soon after that, I found in another picture that she had, a picture of me."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 433160.0,
      "end_time": 437160.0,
      "text": "This guy over here of course is me."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 437160.0,
      "end_time": 439160.0,
      "text": "This man is Robert Moog,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 439160.0,
      "end_time": 441160.0,
      "text": "the inventor of the Moog synthesizer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 441160.0,
      "end_time": 445160.0,
      "text": "who passed away this past August."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 446160.0,
      "end_time": 451160.0,
      "text": "Robert Moog was a generous, kind person, extraordinarily competent engineer."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 451160.0,
      "end_time": 455160.0,
      "text": "A musician who took time from his life to teach me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 457160.0,
      "end_time": 460160.0,
      "text": "a sophomore, a freshman at SUNY Buffalo."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 460160.0,
      "end_time": 465160.0,
      "text": "He&#39;d come up from Trumansburg to teach me"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 465160.0,
      "end_time": 469160.0,
      "text": "not just about the Moog synthesizer, but we&#39;d be sitting there --"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 469160.0,
      "end_time": 472160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m studying physics at the time. This is 1969, 70, 71."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 472160.0,
      "end_time": 474160.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re studying physics, I&#39;m studying physics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 474160.0,
      "end_time": 476160.0,
      "text": "and he&#39;s saying, \"That&#39;s a good thing to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 476160.0,
      "end_time": 478160.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t get caught up in electronic music if you&#39;re doing physics.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 478160.0,
      "end_time": 481160.0,
      "text": "Mentoring me. He&#39;d come up and"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 481160.0,
      "end_time": 485160.0,
      "text": "spend hours and hours with me."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 485160.0,
      "end_time": 488160.0,
      "text": "He wrote a letter of recommendation for me to get into graduate school."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 488160.0,
      "end_time": 490160.0,
      "text": "In the background, my bicycle."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 490160.0,
      "end_time": 493160.0,
      "text": "I realize that this picture was taken at a friend&#39;s living room."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 493160.0,
      "end_time": 496160.0,
      "text": "Bob Moog came by and hauled a whole pile of equipment"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 496160.0,
      "end_time": 498160.0,
      "text": "to show Greg Flint and I things about this."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 498160.0,
      "end_time": 500160.0,
      "text": "We sat around talking about Fourier transforms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 500160.0,
      "end_time": 503160.0,
      "text": "Bessel functions, modulation transfer functions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 503160.0,
      "end_time": 506160.0,
      "text": "stuff like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 508160.0,
      "end_time": 511160.0,
      "text": "Bob&#39;s passing this past summer has been a loss to all of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 511160.0,
      "end_time": 515160.0,
      "text": "Anyone who&#39;s a musician has been profoundly influenced by Robert Moog."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 516159.0,
      "end_time": 518159.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 518159.0,
      "end_time": 523159.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;ll just say what I&#39;m about to do. What I&#39;m about to do --"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 523159.0,
      "end_time": 527160.0,
      "text": "I hope you can recognize that there&#39;s a distorted sine wave,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 527160.0,
      "end_time": 531160.0,
      "text": "almost a triangular wave upon this Hewlett-Packard oscilloscope."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 533160.0,
      "end_time": 537160.0,
      "text": "Oh, cool. I can get to this place over here, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 538160.0,
      "end_time": 540160.0,
      "text": "Kids. Kids is what I&#39;m going to talk about -- is that okay?"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 540160.0,
      "end_time": 544160.0,
      "text": "It says kids over here, that&#39;s what I&#39;d like to talk about."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 544160.0,
      "end_time": 548160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve decided that, for me at least,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 548160.0,
      "end_time": 552160.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t have a big enough head."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 553160.0,
      "end_time": 556160.0,
      "text": "So I think locally and I act locally."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 556160.0,
      "end_time": 560160.0,
      "text": "I feel that the best way I can help out anything is to help out very, very locally."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 560160.0,
      "end_time": 565160.0,
      "text": "So Ph.D. this, and degree there, and the yadda yadda."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 565160.0,
      "end_time": 569160.0,
      "text": "I was talking about this stuff to"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 569160.0,
      "end_time": 571160.0,
      "text": "some schoolteachers about a year ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 571160.0,
      "end_time": 573160.0,
      "text": "And one of them, several of them would come up to me and say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 573160.0,
      "end_time": 575160.0,
      "text": "\"Well, how come you ain&#39;t teaching?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 575160.0,
      "end_time": 576160.0,
      "text": "And I said, \"Well, I&#39;ve taught graduate --"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 576160.0,
      "end_time": 579160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve had graduate students, I&#39;ve taught undergraduate classes.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 579160.0,
      "end_time": 581160.0,
      "text": "No, they said, \"If you&#39;re so into kids and all this stuff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 581160.0,
      "end_time": 584160.0,
      "text": "how come you ain&#39;t over here on the front lines?"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 584160.0,
      "end_time": 588160.0,
      "text": "Put your money where you mouth is.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 588160.0,
      "end_time": 594160.0,
      "text": "Is true. Is true. I teach eighth-grade science four days a week."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 594160.0,
      "end_time": 596160.0,
      "text": "Not just showing up every now and then."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 596160.0,
      "end_time": 600160.0,
      "text": "No, no, no, no, no. I take attendance."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 600160.0,
      "end_time": 603160.0,
      "text": "I take lunch hour. (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 603160.0,
      "end_time": 606160.0,
      "text": "This is not -- no, no, no, this is not claps."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 606160.0,
      "end_time": 610160.0,
      "text": "I strongly suggest that this is a good thing for each of you to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 610160.0,
      "end_time": 612160.0,
      "text": "Not just show up to class every now and then."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 612160.0,
      "end_time": 616160.0,
      "text": "Teach a solid week. Okay, I&#39;m teaching three-quarters time, but good enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 616160.0,
      "end_time": 618160.0,
      "text": "One of the things that I&#39;ve done for my science students"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 618160.0,
      "end_time": 621160.0,
      "text": "is to tell them, \"Look, I&#39;m going to teach you college-level physics."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 621160.0,
      "end_time": 623160.0,
      "text": "No calculus, I&#39;ll cut out that."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 623160.0,
      "end_time": 625160.0,
      "text": "You won&#39;t need to know trig."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 625160.0,
      "end_time": 628160.0,
      "text": "But you will need to know eighth-grade algebra,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 628160.0,
      "end_time": 630160.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re going to do serious experiments."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 630160.0,
      "end_time": 633160.0,
      "text": "None of this open-to-chapter-seven-and-do-all-the-odd-problem-sets."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 633160.0,
      "end_time": 635160.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re going to be doing genuine physics.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 636160.0,
      "end_time": 638160.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s one of the things I thought I&#39;d do right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 638160.0,
      "end_time": 641160.0,
      "text": "(High-pitched tone)"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 641160.0,
      "end_time": 643160.0,
      "text": "Oh, before I even turn that on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 643160.0,
      "end_time": 647160.0,
      "text": "one of the things that we did about three weeks ago in my class --"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 647160.0,
      "end_time": 649160.0,
      "text": "this is through the lens, and one of the things we used a lens for"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 649160.0,
      "end_time": 651160.0,
      "text": "was to measure the speed of light."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 651160.0,
      "end_time": 654160.0,
      "text": "My students in El Cerrito -- with my help, of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 654160.0,
      "end_time": 657160.0,
      "text": "and with the help of a very beat up oscilloscope --"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 657160.0,
      "end_time": 658160.0,
      "text": "measured the speed of light."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 658160.0,
      "end_time": 663160.0,
      "text": "We were off by 25 percent. How many eighth graders do you know of"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 663160.0,
      "end_time": 665160.0,
      "text": "who have measured the speed of light?"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 665160.0,
      "end_time": 668160.0,
      "text": "In addition to that, we&#39;ve measured the speed of sound."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 668160.0,
      "end_time": 670160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d love to measure the speed of light here."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 670160.0,
      "end_time": 672160.0,
      "text": "I was all set to do it and I was thinking, \"Aw man,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 672160.0,
      "end_time": 674160.0,
      "text": "I was just going to impose upon the powers that be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 675160.0,
      "end_time": 676160.0,
      "text": "and measure the speed of light."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 676160.0,
      "end_time": 680160.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m all set to do it. I&#39;m all set to do it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 680160.0,
      "end_time": 684160.0,
      "text": "but then it turns out that to set up here, you have like 10 minutes to set up!"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 684160.0,
      "end_time": 686160.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s no time to do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 686160.0,
      "end_time": 688160.0,
      "text": "So, next time, maybe, I&#39;ll measure the speed of light!"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 688160.0,
      "end_time": 690160.0,
      "text": "But meanwhile, let&#39;s measure the speed of sound!"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 690160.0,
      "end_time": 692160.0,
      "text": "Well, the obvious way to measure the speed of sound"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 692160.0,
      "end_time": 695160.0,
      "text": "is to bounce sound off something and look at the echo."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 695160.0,
      "end_time": 700160.0,
      "text": "But, probably -- one of my students, Ariel [unclear], said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 700160.0,
      "end_time": 703160.0,
      "text": "\"Could we measure the speed of light using the wave equation?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 703160.0,
      "end_time": 705160.0,
      "text": "And all of you know the wave equation is"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 705160.0,
      "end_time": 711160.0,
      "text": "the frequency times the wavelength of any wave ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 711160.0,
      "end_time": 714160.0,
      "text": "is a constant. When the frequency goes up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 714160.0,
      "end_time": 717160.0,
      "text": "the wavelength comes down. Wavelength goes up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 717160.0,
      "end_time": 721160.0,
      "text": "frequency goes down. So, if we have a wave here --"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 722160.0,
      "end_time": 726160.0,
      "text": "over here, that&#39;s what&#39;s interesting --"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 726160.0,
      "end_time": 729160.0,
      "text": "as the pitch goes up, things get closer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 729160.0,
      "end_time": 731160.0,
      "text": "pitch goes down, things stretch out."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 733160.0,
      "end_time": 735160.0,
      "text": "Right? This is simple physics."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 735160.0,
      "end_time": 738160.0,
      "text": "All of you know this from eighth grade, remember?"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 738160.0,
      "end_time": 742160.0,
      "text": "What they didn&#39;t tell you in physics -- in eighth-grade physics --"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 742160.0,
      "end_time": 745160.0,
      "text": "but they should have, and I wish they had,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 745160.0,
      "end_time": 749160.0,
      "text": "was that if you multiply the frequency times the wavelength of sound"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 749160.0,
      "end_time": 753160.0,
      "text": "or light, you get a constant."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 753160.0,
      "end_time": 755160.0,
      "text": "And that constant is the speed of sound."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 756160.0,
      "end_time": 759160.0,
      "text": "So, in order to measure the speed of sound,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 759160.0,
      "end_time": 763160.0,
      "text": "all I&#39;ve got to do is know its frequency. Well, that&#39;s easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 763160.0,
      "end_time": 765160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve got a frequency counter right here."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 765160.0,
      "end_time": 770160.0,
      "text": "Set it up to around A, above A, above A. There&#39;s an A, more or less."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 770160.0,
      "end_time": 774160.0,
      "text": "Now, so I know the frequency."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 775160.0,
      "end_time": 779160.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s 1.76 kilohertz. I measure its wavelength."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 780160.0,
      "end_time": 783160.0,
      "text": "All I need now is to flip on another beam,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 783160.0,
      "end_time": 786160.0,
      "text": "and the bottom beam is me talking, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 786160.0,
      "end_time": 790160.0,
      "text": "So anytime I talk, you&#39;d see it on the screen."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 791160.0,
      "end_time": 795160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll put it over here, and as I move this away from the source,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 795160.0,
      "end_time": 799160.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll notice the spiral."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 800160.0,
      "end_time": 805160.0,
      "text": "The slinky moves. We&#39;re going through different nodes of the wave,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 805160.0,
      "end_time": 807160.0,
      "text": "coming out this way."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 807160.0,
      "end_time": 809160.0,
      "text": "Those of you who are physicists, I hear you rolling your eyes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 809160.0,
      "end_time": 811160.0,
      "text": "but bear with me. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 811160.0,
      "end_time": 814160.0,
      "text": "To measure the wavelength,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 814160.0,
      "end_time": 819160.0,
      "text": "all I need to do is measure the distance from here --"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 820160.0,
      "end_time": 822160.0,
      "text": "one full wave -- over to here."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 822160.0,
      "end_time": 825160.0,
      "text": "From here to here is the wavelength of sound."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 825160.0,
      "end_time": 832160.0,
      "text": "So, I&#39;ll put a measuring tape here, measuring tape here, move it back over to here."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 833160.0,
      "end_time": 837160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve moved the microphone 20 centimeters."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 837160.0,
      "end_time": 842160.0,
      "text": "0.2 meters from here, back to here, 20 centimeters."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 844160.0,
      "end_time": 849160.0,
      "text": "OK, let&#39;s go back to Mr. Elmo."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 850160.0,
      "end_time": 856160.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;ll say the frequency is 1.76 kilohertz, or 1760."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 857160.0,
      "end_time": 861160.0,
      "text": "The wavelength was 0.2 meters."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 861160.0,
      "end_time": 865160.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s figure out what this is."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 865160.0,
      "end_time": 872160.0,
      "text": "(Laughter) (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 873160.0,
      "end_time": 880160.0,
      "text": "1.76 times 0.2 over here is 352 meters per second."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 880160.0,
      "end_time": 886160.0,
      "text": "If you look it up in the book, it&#39;s really 343."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 886160.0,
      "end_time": 888160.0,
      "text": "But, here with kludgy material, and lousy drink --"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 888160.0,
      "end_time": 892160.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve been able to measure the speed of sound to --"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 893160.0,
      "end_time": 894160.0,
      "text": "not bad. Pretty good."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 895160.0,
      "end_time": 899160.0,
      "text": "All of which comes to what I wanted to say."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 900160.0,
      "end_time": 905160.0,
      "text": "Go back to this picture of me a million years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 905160.0,
      "end_time": 910160.0,
      "text": "It was 1971, the Vietnam War was going on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 910160.0,
      "end_time": 913160.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m like, \"Oh my God!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 913160.0,
      "end_time": 916160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m studying physics: Landau, Lipschitz, Resnick and Halliday."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 916160.0,
      "end_time": 918160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going home for a midterm. A riot&#39;s going on on campus."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 918160.0,
      "end_time": 927160.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a riot! Hey, Elmo&#39;s done: off."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 927160.0,
      "end_time": 929160.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a riot going on on campus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 929160.0,
      "end_time": 932160.0,
      "text": "and the police are chasing me, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 932160.0,
      "end_time": 935160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m walking across campus. Cop comes and looks at me and says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 935160.0,
      "end_time": 937160.0,
      "text": "\"You! You&#39;re a student.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 937160.0,
      "end_time": 939160.0,
      "text": "Pulls out a gun. Goes boom!"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 939160.0,
      "end_time": 943160.0,
      "text": "And a tear gas canister the size of a Pepsi can goes by my head. Whoosh!"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 943160.0,
      "end_time": 946160.0,
      "text": "I get a breath of tear gas and I can&#39;t breathe."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 946160.0,
      "end_time": 948160.0,
      "text": "This cop comes after me with a rifle."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 948160.0,
      "end_time": 950160.0,
      "text": "He wants to clunk me over the head!"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 950160.0,
      "end_time": 953160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m saying, \"I got to clear out of here!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 953160.0,
      "end_time": 958160.0,
      "text": "I go running across campus quick as I can. I duck into Hayes Hall."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 959160.0,
      "end_time": 961160.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s one of these bell-tower buildings."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 961160.0,
      "end_time": 962160.0,
      "text": "The cop&#39;s chasing me."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 963160.0,
      "end_time": 965160.0,
      "text": "Chasing me up the first floor, second floor, third floor."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 965160.0,
      "end_time": 966160.0,
      "text": "Chases me into this room."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 966160.0,
      "end_time": 968160.0,
      "text": "The entranceway to the bell tower."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 968160.0,
      "end_time": 970160.0,
      "text": "I slam the door behind me, climb up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 970160.0,
      "end_time": 972160.0,
      "text": "go past this place where I see a pendulum ticking."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 972160.0,
      "end_time": 974160.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m thinking, \"Oh yeah,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 974160.0,
      "end_time": 976160.0,
      "text": "the square root of the length is proportional to its period.\" (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 977160.0,
      "end_time": 979160.0,
      "text": "I keep climbing up, go back."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 979160.0,
      "end_time": 981160.0,
      "text": "I go to a place where a dowel splits off."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 981160.0,
      "end_time": 982160.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a clock, clock, clock, clock."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 982160.0,
      "end_time": 984160.0,
      "text": "The time&#39;s going backwards because I&#39;m inside of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 984160.0,
      "end_time": 988160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m thinking of Lorenz contractions and Einsteinian relativity."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 988160.0,
      "end_time": 991160.0,
      "text": "I climb up, and there&#39;s this place, way in the back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 991160.0,
      "end_time": 993160.0,
      "text": "that you climb up this wooden ladder."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 993160.0,
      "end_time": 995160.0,
      "text": "I pop up the top, and there&#39;s a cupola."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 995160.0,
      "end_time": 997160.0,
      "text": "A dome, one of these ten-foot domes."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 997160.0,
      "end_time": 1000160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m looking out and I&#39;m seeing the cops bashing students&#39; heads,"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 1000160.0,
      "end_time": 1002160.0,
      "text": "shooting tear gas, and watching students throwing bricks."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 1002160.0,
      "end_time": 1005160.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m asking, \"What am I doing here? Why am I here?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 1005160.0,
      "end_time": 1008160.0,
      "text": "Then I remember what my English teacher in high school said."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 1008160.0,
      "end_time": 1012160.0,
      "text": "Namely, that when they cast bells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 1012160.0,
      "end_time": 1015160.0,
      "text": "they write inscriptions on them."
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 1015160.0,
      "end_time": 1019160.0,
      "text": "So, I wipe the pigeon manure off one of the bells, and I look at it."
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 1019160.0,
      "end_time": 1020160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m asking myself, \"Why am I here?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 1022160.0,
      "end_time": 1026159.0,
      "text": "So, at this time, I&#39;d like to tell you the words inscribed"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 1026160.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1030160.0000000001,
      "text": "upon the Hayes Hall tower bells:"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 1030160.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1035160.0000000001,
      "text": "\"All truth is one."
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 1035160.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1041160.0000000001,
      "text": "In this light, may science and religion endeavor here"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 1041160.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1045160.0000000001,
      "text": "for the steady evolution of mankind, from darkness to light,"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 1045160.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1050160.0,
      "text": "from narrowness to broad-mindedness, from prejudice to tolerance."
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 1053160.0,
      "end_time": 1060160.0,
      "text": "It is the voice of life, which calls us to come and learn.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 1061160.0,
      "end_time": 1063160.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    }
  ]
}